{"tid":1819944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人一路睇大選live一路喊？","createTime":"2020-01-11T08:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T09:04:17.000Z","uid":84396,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ea0693ec07c7ca6c34656454f84b2d4e427f7c","tid":1819944,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好羨慕台灣人<br />\n<br />\n無論佢地投邊個都好<br />\n<br />\n佢地有權揀 政府做得好既 人民繼續選<br />\n<br />\n做得差淨係鳩up既 下次就要收皮<br />\n<br />\n人民同政府係有社會契約 相互連結<br />\n<br />\n睇下香港 連最基本人權都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好葡萄 每人都有票去決定國家既未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0766903e18eec42252759d8fc5e114ff8dd82a0c","tid":1819944,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"我想投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff00dffa3ed7291c1337ba12de149e9058d98515","tid":1819944,"uid":246023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"人地以前爭取成功今日先有得投票<br />\n我地都要繼續努力"},{"pid":"6d8100eea0bd3908dea22957a9539fb7bc433cd2","tid":1819944,"uid":143151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家投錯 有機會下屆都收皮<br />\n覺得Korea fish 加 中共 乜都做得出<br />\n所以小英一定要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e7099b147098ea7eec19967956cfb639c729d3","tid":1819944,"uid":293937,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,